author: smuzaffar
body:
`cms_omds_tunnel` tunnal has been remove. See https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/issues/37888 and https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/38074 for more details. Tracker team has setup a new tunnel `cmsonr_lb` and cms-bot has been updated to use correct `tnsnames.ora` to use this tunnel.

This fixes #37888
title: use cmsonr_lb instead of cms_omds_tunnel for SiStrip O2O unit tests
